INSERT INTO `product_desc` VALUES ('155192485269075', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">哪家酒店，能成为世上最著名的赌城拉斯维加斯最大的酒店？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">哪家酒店，在纸醉金迷的澳门，能与大佬葡京赌场称兄道弟？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">——亲，这题太难了，还是给点提示吧：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">好，翠花，上酸菜；不，放雄狮<br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">国际顶级酒店品牌美高梅，以娱乐与奢华体验闻名于世，震慑群雄（众国际顶级酒店）：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268264153405.jpg\" data-original=\"/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268264153405.jpg\" alt=\"/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268264153405.jpg\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">不捏软柿子，只虐最强者：要咆哮，就要在最奢华的两大赌城独领风骚，不服你来咬我啊！<br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">其实，霸气外露的美高梅雄狮，虽然高冷，但有时还是感觉萌萌哒！<br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268885869778.jpg\" data-original=\"/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268885869778.jpg\" alt=\"/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268885869778.jpg\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">现在，美高梅雄狮又瞄上了国内高端酒店最密集的三亚亚龙湾：湾湾的顶级酒店，你们准备好颤抖了吗？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-