INSERT INTO `product_desc` VALUES ('155194804179072', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">哪家酒店，能成为世上最著名的赌城拉斯维加斯最大的酒店？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">哪家酒店，在纸醉金迷的澳门，能与大佬葡京赌场称兄道弟？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">——亲，这题太难了，还是给点提示吧：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">好，翠花，上酸菜；不，放雄狮<br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">国际顶级酒店品牌美高梅，以娱乐与奢华体验闻名于世，震慑群雄（众国际顶级酒店）：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268264153405.jpg\" data-original=\"/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268264153405.jpg\" alt=\"/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268264153405.jpg\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">不捏软柿子，只虐最强者：要咆哮，就要在最奢华的两大赌城独领风骚，不服你来咬我啊！<br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">其实，霸气外露的美高梅雄狮，虽然高冷，但有时还是感觉萌萌哒！<br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268885869778.jpg\" data-original=\"/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268885869778.jpg\" alt=\"/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268885869778.jpg\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; display: inline;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">现在，美高梅雄狮又瞄上了国内高端酒店最密集的三亚亚龙湾：湾湾的顶级酒店，你们准备好颤抖了吗？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><img src=\"http://www.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268896359510.jpg\" data-original=\"/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268896359510.jpg\" alt=\"/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170809/1502268896359510.jpg\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; display: inline;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Long live the lion king！</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\"><strong>三亚亚龙湾美高梅度假酒店介绍</strong><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">与美国拉斯维加斯美高梅酒店（拉斯维加斯最大的酒店）及澳门美高梅酒店同属美国美高梅酒店集团，是这家国际顶级酒店品牌入驻内地的第一家酒店。位于有着温暖气候、细腻白沙、奢华生活的亚龙湾一线海景处。</span></p>', '<div id=\"box-2\" style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-left: 30px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><div style=\"border-left: 1px dashed rgb(216, 110, 80); padding-left: 30px;\"><div id=\"boxs-1\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 2, 2); position: relative;\">Day1行程&nbsp;</h3><div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;\"></div><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 2, 2); position: relative;\"><img src=\"http://www.meilvlx.com/Public/Home/images/lunch_icon.png\" alt=\"用餐\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; left: -47px; top: -4px;\">用餐</h3><div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;\"></div><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 2, 2); position: relative;\"><img src=\"http://www.meilvlx.com/Public/Home/images/hoder_icon.png\" alt=\"住宿\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; left: -47px; top: -4px;\">住宿</h3><div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;\"></div></div></div></div><div id=\"box-3\" style=\"padding-bottom: 26px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><h3 style=\"padding-left: 10px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(204, 94, 79); position: relative;\"><span style=\"width: 5px; background-color: rgb(204, 94, 79); position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; border-radius: 3px;\"></span>费用包含</h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">1、亚龙湾美高梅度假酒店高尔夫景客房1晚住宿，三亚湾红树林度假世界木棉酒店高级房2晚住宿；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">2、广州往返三亚机票（含税及机场建设费）；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">3、两家酒店中的每日中西式豪华自助早餐；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">4、三亚机场至三亚湾红树林木棉酒店的接机服务一次；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">5、免费美高梅炫彩礼遇：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;免费观看成人泳池露天电影；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;免费享用所有公共区域及客房内的高速WIFI；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;免费参与儿童乐园多项免费娱乐项目；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;随房赠送100元水疗代金券；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;免费使用酒店户外海景泳池以及24小时健身房；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;免费使用电子自助航班登机服务（不能托运行李）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">6.可视房态延迟退房至14：00；<br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">7.免费享用酒店的私家泳池、私家园林、私家沙滩等免费设施；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">8. 免费享用酒店公共区域及客房免费WIFI；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">9. 三亚湾红树林度假世界至亚龙湾私属沙滩的固定往返免费穿梭巴士，需提前一天预约；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"padding-left: 10px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(204, 94, 79); position: relative;\"><span style=\"width: 5px; background-color: rgb(204, 94, 79); position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; border-radius: 3px;\"></span>费用不含</h3>1.除包含费用外的一切个人消费。<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p></div>', null, null);
INSERT INTO `product_desc` VALUES ('155194815034494', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 114, 196);\">东省首屈一指。海陵岛被《中国国家地理》杂志评为“中国最美十大海岛”，也是广东省唯一入选的海岛。</span><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(68, 114, 196); font-family: 宋体;\">这里地处</span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/4091709.htm\" style=\"text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 114, 196); font-family: 宋体;\">南亚热带</span></a><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(68, 114, 196); font-family: 宋体;\">，全年</span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/9196.htm\" style=\"text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 114, 196); font-family: 宋体;\">日照</span></a><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(68, 114, 196);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">时间长，年平均气温</span>22.8</span><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 114, 196);\">℃</span><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(68, 114, 196);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，水温</span>23.5</span><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 114, 196);\">℃</span><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(68, 114, 196);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，降雨量</span>1816<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">毫米，年晴天数</span>310<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">天，四季气候宜人，素以阳光灿烂明媚，沙质均匀松软，海水清澈纯净，空气清新纯洁而著称，各类质素均达国际一类（级）标准，又因沙滩宽阔平坦，海浪柔软适中，无</span></span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/5123.htm\" style=\"text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 114, 196); font-family: 宋体;\">鲨鱼</span></a><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(68, 114, 196); font-family: 宋体;\">出没而成为名扬海内外的天然海水浴场。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(68, 114, 196); font-family: 宋体;\"><img src=\"http://tplogin.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180302/1519960199984468.jpg\" data-original=\"http://tplogin.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180302/1519960199984468.jpg\" alt=\"http://tplogin.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180302/1519960199984468.jpg\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; display: inline;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(68, 114, 196); font-family: 宋体;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(68, 114, 196); font-family: 宋体;\"><img src=\"http://tplogin.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180302/1519960208767405.gif\" data-original=\"http://tplogin.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180302/1519960208767405.gif\" alt=\"http://tplogin.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180302/1519960208767405.gif\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; display: inline;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(68, 114, 196); font-family: 宋体;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px;\"><img src=\"http://tplogin.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180302/1519960255123280.gif\" data-original=\"http://tplogin.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180302/1519960255123280.gif\" alt=\"http://tplogin.meilvlx.com/Public/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180302/1519960255123280.gif\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; display: inline;\"></p><p><br></p>', '<div id=\"boxs-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 2, 2); position: relative;\">Day1行程&nbsp;广州—海陵岛</h3><div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">07：30广州地铁1号线杨箕站E1出口集中、08：10在佛山大沥高速路口<br><br>12：00到达闸坡海陵岛后自理午餐（因闸坡海陵岛旺季餐厅十分爆满，为方便游客用餐，导游有代订团餐服务，餐费AA25元-35元/人不等，您也可自行用餐）。<br>13：30后根据客人报名的酒店类型安排办理入住（酒店安排以导游安排为准），后自由活动。闸坡以众多免费公共海滩著称，您可结伴到免费海滩拾贝、踏浪、观海、放风筝、踢沙滩足球、打沙滩排球，一起度过愉快的午后。<br>19：00自理晚餐，建议活动项目有：晚上可于沙滩漫步、踏浪，放烟花、孔明灯等；可到闸坡最商业步行街\"一夜程步行街\"游玩，此步行街相当广州的“上下九”、“北京路”，特产美食应有尽有；也可以自行组织到沙滩边上烧烤、酒吧街体验一下当地的夜生活。</div><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 2, 2); position: relative;\"><img src=\"http://www.meilvlx.com/Public/Home/images/lunch_icon.png\" alt=\"用餐\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; left: -47px; top: -4px;\">用餐</h3><div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">不含</div><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 2, 2); position: relative;\"><img src=\"http://www.meilvlx.com/Public/Home/images/hoder_icon.png\" alt=\"住宿\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; left: -47px; top: -4px;\">住宿</h3><div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">渔林或同级</div></div><div id=\"boxs-2\" style=\"padding-top: 34px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 2, 2); position: relative;\"><img src=\"http://www.meilvlx.com/Public/Home/images/day_icon.png\" alt=\"日期\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; left: -47px; top: -4px;\">Day2行程&nbsp;海陵岛—广州</h3><div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">08：00自理早餐，后自由活动，可提前咨询旅行社或获取一定的海陵岛旅游攻略以方便您参考游玩。<br>11：30退房，后自理午餐。<br>下午14：30前在指定地点集中乘车返程。途经休息站（休息时间20分钟），返回广州后，结束愉快旅程！</div><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 2, 2); position: relative;\"><img src=\"http://www.meilvlx.com/Public/Home/images/lunch_icon.png\" alt=\"用餐\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; left: -47px; top: -4px;\">用餐</h3><div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">不含</div><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 2, 2); position: relative;\"><img src=\"http://www.meilvlx.com/Public/Home/images/hoder_icon.png\" alt=\"住宿\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; left: -47px; top: -4px;\">住宿</h3><div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">温馨的家</div></div>', null, null);
